                             DNSSEC-Tools
                        Is your domain secure?


This directory contains some utility programs for
the validator.

To compile:
	make

To run the test cases for the validator:

        ./validate

To run the validator for a specific query:

        ./validate [-p] [-c CLASS] [-t TYPE] DOMAIN_NAME

     If the -c option is not given, the class is assumed to be IN.
     If the -t option is not given, the type is assumed to be A.

To run gethost:

        ./gethost [-x] <hostname>

To run getaddr:
	./getaddr [-v] [-c] <hostname>
